title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Cronin/Gleeman/Birk/Talkers
description: Bruce Boudreau calls in ahead of tomorrow's Wild game, Courtney Cronin in studio for an hour on Vikings aftermath, Gleeman in studio on Wolves/Twins/Misc, Matt Birk calls in from Florida, with Vikings takes and calls to finish!
